; Tutorial Script for James Conwell's Total Chaos

;testfile

saveboard

addspell growths to 1
erasepage

waitmouseorkey
endmod
hilite 2 up 2 left of player1 wizard
hilite 2 down 2 right of player1 wizard
waitmouseorkey
;1 phase for all wizards
 humanly beginspellcastingphase
 announcespell tempestid from player1
 precastspell tempestid from player1
waitmouseorkey
 player1 castspell tempestid from player1 wizard to 2 up 2 l of player1 wizard
 player1 castspell tempestid from player1 wizard to 2 down 2 right of player1 wizard
 endspellcastingphase

;example
;Player1 CastsSpell 3 ArmourID from Player1's Wizard to Player1's Wizard, Player1's OgreID, Player1's OrcID, Player1's Mind Flayer
WaitMouseOrKey

waitmouseorkey
;only for 1 player
 humanly beginmovementphaseofplayer 1
 clickon my creature
 n,e,s,w,nw,ne,se,sw
 clickoff
;ends current movementphase
 endmovementphase

restoreboard
;playnextthemesong
